item.title: What shall I use?
item.dc:creator: @_Kate1 ,Kate
item.description:
@_Kate1 wrote:

Well we all have different opinions for different server sources, so there really is not any “best” server. But why not look for one you’ll find easy to code, such as a decent 317, or even DeltaScape - they’re known as the easiest to code. I would then move on up to 370’s, 474’s, etc as you get better and better at managing servers.

Nevertheless, It’s really up to you. My recommendation to start off, is DeltaScape.
